gen_id <- function(x) {
  id <- data.frame(matrix(unlist(strsplit(row.names(x), "_", fixed = TRUE)), ncol = 3, byrow = T))
  colnames(id) <- c("Author", "intervention", "Outcome")
  data.frame(cbind(id, x))
}

numb_out_miss <- function(x) {
  data.frame(N_out = nrow(x),
             incl_out = paste(mainsympt[which(mainsympt %in% unique(subset(x, x$Outcome %in% mainsympt)$Outcome))], collapse = ', '),
             missing_out = paste(mainsympt[which(!(mainsympt %in% unique(subset(x, x$Outcome %in% mainsympt)$Outcome)))], collapse = ', '))
}

nout <- function(x) {
  data.frame(
    ASD = sum(grepl("Overall ASD symptoms", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    SC = sum(grepl("Social communication", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    RRB = sum(grepl("Restricted repetitive behaviors", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    AB = sum(grepl("Adaptive behaviors", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    IQ = sum(grepl("Cognition(IQ)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    nvIQ = sum(grepl("Cognition(nonverbal IQ)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    LT = sum(grepl("Language", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)) - sum(grepl("Language(Expressive)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)) - sum(grepl("Language(Receptive)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    LE = sum(grepl("Language(Expressive)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    LR = sum(grepl("Language(Receptive)", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)),
    DIS = sum(grepl("Disruptive behaviors", x$Outcome, fixed = TRUE)))
}

rename_outcome <- function(x) {
  x[x == "Restricted repetitive behaviors"] <- "Repetitive behav."
  x[x == "Adaptive behaviors"] <- "Adaptive behav."
  x[x == "Cognition(IQ)"] <- "Cognition (IQ)"
  x[x == "Cognition(nonverbal IQ)"] <- "Cognition (n.v. IQ)"
  x[x == "Overall ASD symptoms"] <- "Overall ASD sympt."
  x[x == "Language(Receptive)"] <- "Language (Rec)"
  x[x == "Language(Expressive)"] <- "Language (Exp)"
  x[x == "Disruptive behaviors"] <- "Disruptive behav."
  x[x == "Social communication"] <- "Social-communic."
  x
}

B. Main analysis

B.1. Data analysis

umb.main <- metaumbrella::umbrella(df, mult.level = TRUE, method.var = "REML")

res.transit <- metaumbrella::add.evidence(umb.main, 
    criteria = "Personalised",
    class_I = c(cases = 1000, p.value = 1e-6, I2 = 50,
                egger = .05, 
                rob = 75, amstar = 4),
    class_II = c(cases = 200, p.value = 1e-6, 
                largest = "not_null", 
                rob = 50, amstar = 3),
    class_III = c(cases = 100, p.value = 1e-3),
    class_IV = c(p.value = 5e-2))

res <- gen_id(metaumbrella::summary.umbrella(res.transit))
res$Total_n <- round(res$Total_n)
res$factor <- with(res, paste0(Author, "_", intervention, "_", Outcome))
res$Class <- ifelse(res$Class == "V", "ns", as.character(res$Class))

res.main <- merge(res, df.tot, by = "factor")

ci_lo_transit <- ci_up_transit <- CI_up <- CI_lo <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.main)) {
  ci_lo_transit[i] <- gsub(",.*", "", res.main$value_CI[i])
  ci_up_transit[i] <- gsub(".*, ", "", res.main$value_CI[i])
  CI_lo[i] <- gsub("\\(", "", ci_lo_transit[i])
  CI_up[i] <- gsub(")", "", ci_up_transit[i])
}

CI_lo <- as.numeric(as.character(CI_lo))
CI_up <- as.numeric(as.character(CI_up))
res.main$se <- (CI_up - CI_lo) / 3.92

res.main$Sample_size_studies <- with(res.main, paste0(Total_n, " (", n_studies, ")"))
res.main$Effect_size <- paste0("SMD = ", res.main$value, " [", CI_lo, ", ", CI_up, ")")

res.main$Risk_of_bias <- with(res.main,
      ifelse(rob < 50, "High", # (>= 50% studies)
        ifelse(rob < 75, "Med.", # (25-50 % studies)
          ifelse(rob >= 75, "Low", # (< 25% studies)
                 NA_real_))))

res.main$Setting <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.main)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.main$sett_home[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.main$sett_clin[i]) |
      !is.nan(res.main$sett_class[i])) {
    res.main$Setting[i] <- c("Home", "Clinic", "Classroom")[which.max(c(res.main$sett_home[i], res.main$sett_clin[i], res.main$sett_class[i]))]
  } else {
    res.main$Setting[i] <- NA
  }
}
    
res.main$Implementer <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.main)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.main$prof_imp[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.main$parent_imp[i])) {
    res.main$Implementer[i] <- c("Profesionnal", "Caregiver")[which.max(c(res.main$prof_imp[i], res.main$parent_imp[i]))]
  } else {
    res.main$Implementer[i] <- NA
  }
}
  
  
res.main$Type_of_outcome <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.main)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.main$Outcome_test[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.main$Outcome_questionnaire[i]) |
      !is.nan(res.main$Outcome_observation[i])) {
    res.main$Type_of_outcome[i] <- c("Test", "Reporting", "Observation")[which.max(c(res.main$Outcome_test[i], res.main$Outcome_questionnaire[i], res.main$Outcome_observation[i]))]
  } else {
    res.main$Type_of_outcome[i] <- NA
  }
}

res.main$Active_controls <- paste0(round(res.main$Active_controls), "%")
display.cols <- c("Paper", "Intervention", "Outcome", "Class", 'Sample size (studies)',

Data analysis

umb.S1 <- metaumbrella::umbrella(df.S1, mult.level = TRUE, method.var = "REML", r = 0.8)

res.transit.S1 <- metaumbrella::add.evidence(umb.S1, 
    criteria = "Personalised",
    class_I = c(cases = 1000, p.value = 1e-6, I2 = 50,
                pi = "not_null", egger = .05, 
                rob = 75, amstar = 4),
    class_II = c(cases = 200, p.value = 1e-6, 
                largest = "not_null", 
                rob = 50, amstar = 3),
    class_III = c(cases = 100, p.value = 1e-3),
    class_IV = c(p.value = 5e-2))

res.transit.S1 <- gen_id(metaumbrella::summary.umbrella(res.transit.S1))
res.transit.S1$Total_n <- round(res.transit.S1$Total_n)

res.transit.S1$Class <- ifelse(res.transit.S1$Class == "V", "ns", as.character(res.transit.S1$Class))

res.transit.S1$factor <- with(res.transit.S1, paste0(Author, "_", intervention, "_", Outcome))

res.S1 <- merge(res.transit.S1, df.tot.S1, by = "factor")
res.S1$Sample_size_studies <- paste0(res.S1$Total_n, " (", res.S1$n_studies, ")")

ci_lo_transit_S1 <- ci_up_transit_S1 <- CI_up_S1 <- CI_lo_S1 <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.S1)) {
  ci_lo_transit_S1[i] <- gsub(",.*", "", res.S1$value_CI[i])
  ci_up_transit_S1[i] <- gsub(".*, ", "", res.S1$value_CI[i])
  CI_lo_S1[i] <- gsub("\\(", "", ci_lo_transit_S1[i])
  CI_up_S1[i] <- gsub(")", "", ci_up_transit_S1[i])
}

CI_lo_S1 <- as.numeric(as.character(CI_lo_S1))
CI_up_S1 <- as.numeric(as.character(CI_up_S1))
res.S1$Effect_size <- paste0("SMD = ", res.S1$value, " [", CI_lo_S1, ", ", CI_up_S1, "]")
res.S1$se <- with(res.S1, (CI_up_S1 - CI_lo_S1) / 3.92)

res.S1$Risk_of_bias <- with(res.S1,
      ifelse(rob <= 50, "High", # (>= 50% studies)
        ifelse(rob <= 75, "Moderate", # (25-50 % studies)
          ifelse(rob > 75, "Low", # (< 25% studies)
                 NA_real_))))

res.S1$Setting <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.S1)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.S1$sett_home[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.S1$sett_clin[i]) |
      !is.nan(res.S1$sett_class[i])) {
    res.S1$Setting[i] <- c("Home", "Clinic", "Classroom")[which.max(c(res.S1$sett_home[i], res.S1$sett_clin[i], res.S1$sett_class[i]))]
  } else {
    res.S1$Setting[i] <- NA
  }
}
    
res.S1$Implementer <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.S1)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.S1$prof_imp[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.S1$parent_imp[i])) {
    res.S1$Implementer[i] <- c("Profesionnal", "Caregiver")[which.max(c(res.S1$prof_imp[i], res.S1$parent_imp[i]))]
  } else {
    res.S1$Implementer[i] <- NA
  }
}
  
  
res.S1$Type_of_outcome <- NA
for (i in 1:nrow(res.S1)) {
  if (!is.nan(res.S1$Outcome_test[i]) | 
      !is.nan(res.S1$Outcome_questionnaire[i]) |
      !is.nan(res.S1$Outcome_observation[i])) {
    res.S1$Type_of_outcome[i] <- c("Test", "Reporting", "Observation")[which.max(c(res.S1$Outcome_test[i], res.S1$Outcome_questionnaire[i], res.S1$Outcome_observation[i]))]
  } else {
    res.S1$Type_of_outcome[i] <- NA
  }
}

res.S1$Intervention <- gsub("\\s*\\([^\\)]+\\)","", res.S1$Intervention)

Discrepancy

df.NDBI.disc <- subset(df, Outcome_general == "Overall ASD symptoms" & Intervention %in% c("PRT", "ESDM", "NDBI"))

NDBI.dup <- data.frame(
  meta = df.NDBI.disc$First_author_meta,
  author = df.NDBI.disc$author,
  dup = duplicated(df.NDBI.disc$author) | duplicated(df.NDBI.disc$author, fromLast = TRUE))

NDBI.dup$author_keep = 0
NDBI.dup$row <- 1:nrow(NDBI.dup)

for (aut in unique(NDBI.dup$author)) {
  sub <- which(NDBI.dup$author == aut)
  if (any(NDBI.dup$dup[sub]) == TRUE & "Crank" %in% NDBI.dup$meta[sub]) {
    NDBI.dup$author_keep[which(NDBI.dup$author == aut & NDBI.dup$meta == "Crank")] = 1
    } else if (any(NDBI.dup$dup[sub]) == TRUE & "Tiede" %in% NDBI.dup$meta[sub]) {
    NDBI.dup$author_keep[which(NDBI.dup$author == aut & NDBI.dup$meta == "Tiede")] = 1
    } else if (any(NDBI.dup$dup[sub]) == TRUE & "Fuller" %in% NDBI.dup$meta[sub]) {
    NDBI.dup$author_keep[which(NDBI.dup$author == aut & NDBI.dup$meta == "Fuller")] = 1
    } else if (all(NDBI.dup$dup[sub]) == FALSE) {
      NDBI.dup$author_keep[which(NDBI.dup$author == aut)] <- 1
    }
}

df.NDBI.disc <- df.NDBI.disc[which(NDBI.dup$author_keep == 1), ]

df.NDBI.disc$factor <- "NDBI"; df.NDBI.disc$amstar = min(df.NDBI.disc$amstar)


umb.NDBI.disc <- metaumbrella::umbrella(df.NDBI.disc, mult.level = TRUE)
